{"tid":128692,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 –冬菇燜鵝掌（智能煲製作）","createTime":"2017-02-21T04:41:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T03:11:11.000Z","uid":30742,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"138c45c9ae31b443161bce7ae0813ea3918d2978","tid":128692,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T04:41:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/Hw3MT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHw3MT.jpg&h=28167f47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我老豆平時都好鍾意燜鵝掌<br />\n但我一d都唔鍾意食，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知點解佢好鍾意買炸好果d再燜到好淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上個月去人地屋企食團年飯，竟然食到爽口彈牙既鵝掌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我又唔好意思問人地點整<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後fanspage有朋友問我點整&hellip;攪到我囉囉攣&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n終於都係上星期試整左一次，其實用智能煲整好方便，<br />\n不過缺點係難控制火候，呢次我都仲係覺得淋左d<br />\n但味道係夠既，如果係鍾意平常出街既口味，呢個就岩架喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我下次會再縮短d時間，希望唔好咁淋啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMy fanspage:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=7b359366\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nMy blog:<a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=0e4ddc27\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a><br />\nig: _oldlady_<br />\n冬菇燜鵝掌：<a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/02/blog-post_20.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F02%2Fblog-post_20.html&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=05df0851\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/02/blog-post_20.html</a>"},{"pid":"14f80f98c5e2af71ea35beff3454118e53cd5527","tid":128692,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T04:41:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be15d7f3161202d04af7ee5357ca63c825b4659b","tid":128692,"uid":64564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T04:41:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d928e61001405ad7aa97677b6c09ce29871c20f","tid":128692,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T04:44:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41037a62f54d3ba2600d1504dd5e43e91eaa28ab","tid":128692,"uid":44089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T04:55:48.000Z","msg":"老娘有冇諗過拍片上Youtube教人煮野食,我諗你個名氣吸引到唔少fans"},{"pid":"c43e953d41266b1e5d2756da0dd469ba85f5d75f","tid":128692,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:17:29.000Z","msg":"好靚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi